      "speakers": [
        "薛应龙"
      ],
      "text": "万事皆由命，半点不由人。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01040006_e00003",
      "play_id": "01040006",
      "scene_id": "01040006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛应龙"
      ],
      "text": "俺，薛应龙。自进唐营并无半点之功。今日芦花河摆下无名大阵，不免单人独马前去破阵，岂不是好！不如盗了老马，出营去罢。",
      "text_length": 57
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01040006_e00004",
      "play_id": "01040006",
      "scene_id": "01040006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "秦汉、窦一虎同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01040006_e00005",
      "play_id": "01040006",
      "scene_id": "01040006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦汉"
      ],
      "text": "小本官往哪里去？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01040006_e00006",
      "play_id": "01040006",
      "scene_id": "01040006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛应龙"
      ],
      "text": "前去破阵！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01040006_e00007",
      "play_id": "01040006",
      "scene_id": "01040006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "窦一虎"
      ],
      "text": "元帅有令，叫你不要出兵。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01040006_e00008",
      "play_id": "01040006",
      "scene_id": "01040006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "薛应龙"
      ],
      "text": "此回出兵，破得此阵便罢！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01040006_e00009",
      "play_id": "01040006",
      "scene_id": "01040006_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
